text: The Family Jewels is a 1965 American comedy movie directed by Jerry Lewis (who also played seven roles in the movie) and starring Donna Butterworth, Sebastian Cabot, Neil Hamilton, Jay Adler. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures and was nominated for 1 Golden Globe in 1966. == Other websites == * Category:1965 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Jerry Lewis Category:Paramount Pictures movies
